\newlabel{fig:policy-breadth}{{4}{6}{First-stage eviction-policy sensitivity on MQ-NIAH-4Q ($n{=}24$, $\bbase {=}16{,}384$). Curves show exact $Q_2$ gain over each policy's matched no-repair baseline. The gray band spans Random-$K$/Oldest-$K$ gains}{figure.caption.5}{}}
